trans-unit.source: Raises an <xref:System.Exception> for a missing event parameter in a <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebClass"></xref>.

The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebClass> class is used by the upgrade tools to upgrade a Visual Basic 6.0 `WebClass` project to an [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] Web-site project.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebClassCouldNotFindEvent"></xref> class.

The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebClass> class is used by the upgrade tools to upgrade a Visual Basic 6.0 `WebClass` project to an [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] Web-site project.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebClassCouldNotFindEvent"></xref> class.

The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebClass> class is used by the upgrade tools to upgrade a Visual Basic 6.0 `WebClass` project to an [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] Web-site project.
A <xref:System.String> that contains the name of the missing event parameter.
